  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced and FUN!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Point and click, super simple controls for an Enjoyable Escape-room puzzle game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/f92b40dbb61d328321c9ba4023e9d34f.poster.avif?t=1733631584\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/f92b40dbb61d328321c9ba4023e9d34f.webm?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/f92b40dbb61d328321c9ba4023e9d34f.mp4?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong>A psychedelic and adorable escape game featuring hand-drawn illustrations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With intuitive point-and-click controls, this game delivers a smooth and satisfying puzzle experience for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/0a300a905b04f6ad9c9305207d5b36a2.poster.avif?t=1733631584\" width=630 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/0a300a905b04f6ad9c9305207d5b36a2.webm?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/0a300a905b04f6ad9c9305207d5b36a2.mp4?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fast and Easy Game-play! Intuitive click-based controls make it stress-free to play.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Psychedelic and Cute Design! Unique, colorful, hand-drawn illustrations.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Refreshing Puzzles! Satisfying puzzles that keep you moving forward with ease.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Short but Fulfilling! A compact yet rich experience with five engaging chapters.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Exciting Original Music! A whimsical soundtrack that enhances your adventure.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/1dd23a3e6ee98c090158648ac1f991f5.poster.avif?t=1733631584\" width=630 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/1dd23a3e6ee98c090158648ac1f991f5.webm?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/1dd23a3e6ee98c090158648ac1f991f5.mp4?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Perfect for players who want a quick, delightful escape! Enjoy the fun, fast-paced puzzle-solving and vibrant visuals in this one-of-a-kind game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced and FUN!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Point and click, super simple controls for an Enjoyable Escape-room puzzle game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/f92b40dbb61d328321c9ba4023e9d34f.poster.avif?t=1733631584\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/f92b40dbb61d328321c9ba4023e9d34f.webm?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/f92b40dbb61d328321c9ba4023e9d34f.mp4?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong>A psychedelic and adorable escape game featuring hand-drawn illustrations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With intuitive point-and-click controls, this game delivers a smooth and satisfying puzzle experience for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/0a300a905b04f6ad9c9305207d5b36a2.poster.avif?t=1733631584\" width=630 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/0a300a905b04f6ad9c9305207d5b36a2.webm?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773010/extras/0a300a905b04f6ad9c9305207d5b36a2.mp4?t=1733631584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fast and Easy Game-play! Intuitive click-based controls make it stress-free to play.  </p><p class=\"bb_